snippet.title: SEGA AGES Ichidant-R & Columns II | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
It's time to put your intellect to the test! Ichidant-R and Columns II are now available as part of the SEGA AGES line-up for Nintendo Switch!

Official website: https://segaages.sega.com/
